{"type":null,"faqId":48083,"title":"更改锁屏风格","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{font-weight:bold;}\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.41527778in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.110416666in;margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">图案解锁</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"解锁\"XE \"图案\"XE \"图案解锁\"XE \"图片解锁\"</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">1.  </span><span>在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178132\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“设置”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">2.  </span><span>在“全部设置”页签下，点击“锁屏和密码”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">3.  </span><span>点击“锁屏密码 &gt; 图案密码”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">4.  </span><span>连接至少四个点绘制图案，然后再次绘制图案进行确认。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">5.  </span><span>设置备用数字密码。当您忘记解锁图案时，可输入该数字密码完成解锁。</span><a name=\"_task_pin_unlock-chtext\"></a>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\"> 数字密码解锁</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"密码\"XE \"数字密码\"XE \"数字解锁\"XE \"解锁\"</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>1.在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178133\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“设置”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>2.在“全部设置”页签下，点击“锁屏和密码”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>3.点击“锁屏密码 &gt; 数字密码”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>4.输入至少四位数字，然后再次输入进行确认。</span><a name=\"_task_password_unlock-chtext\"></a>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\"> 混合密码解锁</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"解锁\"XE \"密码解锁\"XE \"混合密码\"XE \"密码\"</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>1.在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178134\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“设置”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>2.在“全部设置”页签下，点击“锁屏和密码”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>3.点击“锁屏密码 &gt; 混合密码”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>4.按要求输入包含至少四个字符的混合密码，然后再次输入进行确认。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":143,"faqType":"系统功能与设置","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"3669","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-System-Settings","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1445598114000,"seriesProductName":"RIO-AL00,RIO-CL00,RIO-TL00,RIO-UL00,RIO-UL10","visitedTimes":71,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}